title: Discuss amongst yourselves
author: VD
content_html: And in other news, Tarvaris Jackson really does not look as if he’s going to cut it. I’m getting definite Quincy Clark vibe from him. And I’m still pretty dubious about Childress as well. Why does he keep having Jackson drop back and throw when he’s only completed two passes over three quarters and a sack will take them out of FG range?
